<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">Se realiz&oacute; m&uacute;ltiples cortes longitudinales, transversales y oblicuos en un ec&oacute;grafo sectorial de alta resoluci&oacute;n, en tiempo real y sistema doppler color pulsado simultaneo.</span></p>
<ul type="disc">
<li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-language: ES-EC;">El sistema se completa con Elastografia por Shear wave.</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">H&iacute;gado heterog&eacute;neo difuso de aspecto fibroso, no se observa lesiones solidas ni qu&iacute;sticas en su estructura.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">V&iacute;a Biliar intra-extra-hep&aacute;tica de calibre conservado.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">Vena porta permeable de calibre normal con flujo hepatopetal (registro Doppler por encima de la l&iacute;nea basal) pero con velocidades disminuidas (Vm = 11 cm/s) y leve p&eacute;rdida de la &ldquo;fasicidad&rdquo;.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">Ves&iacute;cula AUSENTE (quir&uacute;rgico).</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">No l&iacute;quido libre en cavidad.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">Bazo de forma y tamano normal sin lesiones solidas aleda&ntilde;as.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>
